%N A394009 Decimal expansion of Product_{p prime} (1-1/p)^2 * (1 + 2 * Sum_{k >= 0} 1/p^(2^k)).
%C A394009 The asymptotic probability that two positive integers selected independently at random are coprime and both are exponentially 2^n numbers (A138302).
%F A394009 Equals A271727^2 * A394010.
%e A394009 0.500993677671021447977570913356513912901140108067308...
%o A394009 (PARI) c(m) = prodeulerrat((1-1/p)^2 * (1 + 2 * sum(k = 0, m, 1/p^(2^k))));
%o A394009 {my(c1 = 0, c2 = 1, m = 1); while(c2 != c1, c1 = c2; c2 = c(m); m++); c2}
